text: Asad Khan (born 6 November 1997) is an Afghan cricketer. He made his List A debut for Logar Province in the 2019 Afghanistan Provincial Challenge Cup tournament on 1 August 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Afghan cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
